<BlogPost
  title="The Lung That Failed and What It Taught Us About AI"
  description="A biotech firm saved millions by turning messy data into predictions. Learn how OpenTeams helped them own their AI infrastructure, before it failed."
  date="2025-05-23"
  deck="How a $13B biotech company turned a wall of dead data into a predictive engine for saving lives, with help from Quansight & OpenTeams."
